    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tiddlywinks is a game where round chips or discs called "winks" have to be shot into a bin, pot or scoreboard. This is done by pressing a chip on the edge of another chip so that it jumps into the air.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
